snippet: Two Israeli men were wounded in an attack in a West Bank supermarket, and the suspect was shot and wounded by an off-duty guard who was shopping there.
abstract: Palestinian teenager Ibrahim Salim Abu Sneineh stabs two middle-age Israeli men at supermarket in occupied West Bank before being shot and wounded by off-duty security guard.
lead_paragraph: Two Israeli men were wounded in an attack in a West Bank supermarket, and the suspect was shot and wounded by an off-duty guard who was shopping there.

headline.main: Palestinian Teenager Accused of Stabbing 2 Israelis
headline.print_headline: Two Israelis Stabbed in West Bank
